---
/**
 * Design System - hub · /design-system/
 * Internal tooling docs (noindex). The export artifact for the Figma round-trip.
 * Two documentation pages: the honest as-built inventory ("current") and the
 * consolidated, live-token system ("proposed" - the Figma artifact).
 */
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Design System - Documentation Hub',
  description:
    'Internal design-system documentation for Shriram Financial Services: the honest as-built style inventory of the legacy site, and the consolidated token system rendered live from styles.css for the Figma round-trip.',
  path: '/design-system/',
  noindex: true,
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ================= HERO ================= -->
  <section class="hero" id="sec-hero" data-section="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="ds-eyebrow">Internal · design-system tooling</p>
        <h1>Design <span class="g">System</span></h1>
        <p class="lead">
          The export artifact for the Figma round-trip. Two documentation pages: the honest
          record of what the legacy site actually rendered, and the consolidated token system
          rendered live from <code>styles.css</code> so it can never drift.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= THE TWO DOCS ================= -->
  <section class="section sec-light" id="sec-docs" data-section="docs">
    <div class="ds-intro">
      <h2 class="sec-title">Two views of one system</h2>
      <p class="sec-lead">
        The audit (<code>docs/legacy-style-audit.md</code>) inventoried every style value in the
        legacy static site - roughly 150 colors across two parallel stylesheets. The token system
        in <code>src/styles/global.css</code> resolves that sprawl. These two pages are the
        before &amp; after: <b>Current</b> is the honest mirror of what was; <b>Proposed</b> is
        the clean system, rendered live, ready to become Figma variables.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="ds-cards">
      <a class="ds-card" href="/design-system/current/">
        <span class="ds-card-tag">Doc 1 · the “before”</span>
        <h3>What is used</h3>
        <p>
          The honest as-built inventory extracted from the full audit - ~150 colors grouped into
          near-duplicate clusters, the two-stylesheet fork, and the off-scale type / off-grid
          spacing the token system corrects. Values here are historical literals.
        </p>
        <span class="ds-card-go">
          Open the inventory
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
        </span>
      </a>

      <a class="ds-card ds-card--primary" href="/design-system/proposed/">
        <span class="ds-card-tag">Doc 2 · the Figma artifact</span>
        <h3>What is suggested</h3>
        <p>
          The consolidated, duplication-proofed system rendered <b>live from the tokens</b> -
          primitive → semantic → component, a full colour/type/spacing/shadow reference and a
          component gallery. Structured to map 1:1 onto Figma variables for the round-trip.
        </p>
        <span class="ds-card-go">
          Open the system
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .ds-eyebrow {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold-400);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .hero code,
  .ds-intro code {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .hero code {
    color: var(--color-gold-200);
  }
  .ds-intro code {
    color: var(--color-text-heading-dark);
  }

  .ds-intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .ds-intro b {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .ds-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .ds-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    background: var(--color-surface-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-card);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      background 0.25s ease,
      border-color 0.25s ease,
      transform 0.25s ease;
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) and (hover: hover) {
    .ds-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-tan-400);
    background: var(--color-cream-300);
  }
  }
  .ds-card--primary {
    background: var(--color-surface-dark-card);
    border-color: var(--color-surface-dark-card);
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) and (hover: hover) {
    .ds-card--primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-olive-925);
    border-color: var(--color-olive-700);
  }
  }
  .ds-card-tag {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .ds-card--primary .ds-card-tag {
    color: var(--color-gold-400);
  }
  .ds-card h3 {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--color-text-heading-dark);
  }
  .ds-card--primary h3 {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  .ds-card p {
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }
  .ds-card--primary p {
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark-body);
  }
  .ds-card p b {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  .ds-card--primary p b {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  .ds-card-go {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-text-heading-dark);
  }
  .ds-card--primary .ds-card-go {
    color: var(--color-gold-400);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ds-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ds-card {
      padding: 32px;
    }
    .ds-card h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
